==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stereoelectric
<hw>Ste`re*o*e*lec"tric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Stereo-</ets> + <ets>electric</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the generation of
electricity by means of solid bodies alone; <as>as, a
<ex>stereoelectric</ex> current is one obtained by means of solids,
without any liquid</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stereogram</ent>⟦br⟧
